                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#gasperini2000"/>, p. <citedRange>31</citedRange></bibl> 
                    (= <bibl><ptr target="#gasperini2008"/>, pp. <citedRange>452-454</citedRange></bibl>).
                    
                </p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
